subject: College Athletics
NCAA Basketball Tournament
lead_paragraph: When the Gators lost in the first round of the Southeastern Conference tournament, they knew it would keep them out of the N.C.A.A. tournament field. They had no idea it would also get them kicked out of their practice facility.
